body:
so i was given a PBE account by older brother because he left for college and quit league entirely. but i was on it yesterday and then i tried to log on this morning and it proceeded to say "account inactive" even though i was just on it yesterday, so im really confused and just want the account back. its been helping me improve my game on the regular servers because i have access to try to runes and masteries and new builds on champs, i would really love to continue using the account, hopefully riot can get back to me and resolve the issue.

oh i also tried the whole email recovery &amp; password but unfortunately my brothers email and password is secure and with him studying abroad in germany i havent been in contact with him in over 4 months and wont be for the next year and half. 
so if i could get my acccount back and change the email and password to mine maybe that would help? still need riots support on this. {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
